方案以及新冠疫情肆虐，使斯里兰卡的公共债务负担不可持续，而旅游业的崩溃导致外汇收入暴跌。同时，在能源价格上涨的冲击下，燃料供应稀缺导致政府不得不实施限电，政府办公室和学校已处于关闭状态。 联合国此前指出，在6月，斯里兰卡的整体通胀率达到54.6%，为1954年以来的最高水平，粮食安全、农业、生计和卫生部门首当其冲。外媒：抗议者冲入斯里兰卡总统官邸|界面新闻 · 快讯"},"attached_info":"Cj8Inb+gzrDV+8FxEAMaCDgyODEyOTYyIP6ApZYGMB04jAVAAXIJNTQyMzg5MTkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"606 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-52d5e34f2a03ee2d577fde4ea40ba6af_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1657414415.7954926","card_id":"Q_542340730","target":{"id":542340730,"title":"为什么看完电影《咒》的大部分观众都很生气，甚至觉得晦气？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/542340730","type":"question","created":1657328977,"answer_count":137,"follower_count":269,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18833,21790,761502],"comment_count":16,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Inb+gzrDV+8FxEAMaCDgyODAyMjQwINGqo5YGMBA4jQJAAnIJNTQyMzQwNzMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"579 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-22f8eb287aae50d753d7b00956b2d89b_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1657414415.7961357","card_id":"Q_542175401","target":{"id":542175401,"title":"长城汽车高管「炮轰」华为余承东，表示再大的嘴也不能大放厥词，你认为余承东是否会对此做出回应？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/542175401","type":"question","created":1657248261,"answer_count":166,"follower_count":430,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[140,4220,5263,44177,94173],"comment_count":24,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"7月6日，长城汽车魏牌CEO李瑞峰发微博称：“打铁还需自身硬，增程式混动技术落后是行业共识，再大的嘴，也不能大放厥词。” 并在博文后附上话题词#余承东称增程车不够先进是胡扯#，同时配上了“我想不通”的图片。 长城汽车高管“炮轰”华为余承东：再大的嘴，也不能大放厥词"},"attached_info